---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "SMEG Dishwasher Repair | Southern California | Italian FAB Family";
const description = "SMEG dishwasher repair across Southern California — Italian Bermani family Guastalla 1948, FAB retro color-matched, Linea built-in. Silver Lake + Los Feliz design angle. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/smeg-dishwasher-repair/";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Is SMEG really still independent Italian family-owned?",
    a: "Yes, and this genuinely matters for service context. SMEG is the Bermani family's Italian appliance company, founded 1948 in Guastalla, Emilia-Romagna, and still controlled by the Bermani family through three generations. Unlike most European appliance brands that have been consolidated into global conglomerates (Whirlpool, Electrolux, BSH, Haier, Arçelik), SMEG is independent — no corporate parent, Bermani family ownership, Guastalla factory. For LA repair service, the implication is parts-chain specificity: SMEG parts don't cross-reference with broader European parents. Our techs source through SMEG USA's distribution (operated from Fairfield NJ) for service parts. Lead times: common items 3-7 days; specialty color-matched or retro-specific items 7-14 days. Worth understanding because a 'European dishwasher parts' approach that works for Bosch (BSH) or Miele won't apply to SMEG."
  },
  {
    q: "I'm shopping for SMEG because I like the FAB retro fridge look — do they make dishwashers?",
    a: "Yes, SMEG's dishwasher line covers both FAB-aesthetic retro-styled units and their mainstream Linea built-in line. FAB dishwashers are less common than FAB refrigerators (the FAB line was built around refrigeration as the flagship) but they exist — typically coordinated color-matched with a FAB fridge installation in design-forward Silver Lake, Los Feliz, Highland Park, Mount Washington, and Atwater Village kitchens where the kitchen's visual identity matters as much as function. More common for LA SMEG dishwasher installs: Linea built-in (mainstream European-spec stainless-interior dishwasher, 24-inch standard width, panel-ready or stainless-front) that ships with a FAB refrigerator in the same household as complementary design-forward specs. Service profiles for FAB retro and Linea built-in differ on trim hardware and retro-specific color-matching but share refrigeration-cycle-equivalent core service logic."
  },
  {
    q: "What are the most common SMEG dishwashers in LA?",
    a: "By volume, Linea built-in 24-inch models dominate LA SMEG dishwasher service — LSA series and related. These are European-spec built-in dishwashers with stainless-steel tubs, 43-47 dB noise profiles, fully-integrated panel-ready option, and standard 24-inch cabinetry fit. Less common but distinctive: FAB-retro-aesthetic dishwasher models that color-coordinate with FAB refrigerators (less widespread than the refrigerator line but appear in coordinated SMEG-suite kitchen installs). SMEG compact 18-inch dishwasher models are rare in the US — not a significant volume product. Panel-ready integration is the typical LA SMEG dishwasher configuration, since most LA homeowners who spec SMEG dishwashers are doing so as part of a broader SMEG-appliance-suite install where cabinetry-integration aesthetic matters."
  },
  {
    q: "SMEG dishwasher won't drain — how is the diagnostic different from a Bosch or Samsung?",
    a: "Platform-specific, and worth flagging the differences. SMEG's drain system uses a dedicated pump architecture distinct from BSH (Bosch / Thermador) or Whirlpool (KitchenAid / Maytag) platforms. Diagnostic order: (1) drain filter at bottom of tub — same first check as any dishwasher; clean thoroughly; 50-60% of no-drain calls resolve here; (2) drain pump impeller — SMEG uses a specific Italian-sourced pump; our dispatch carries SMEG pump spares but specialty variants are 7-day lead; pump swap $280–$420; (3) drain-hose routing — SMEG built-in installs sometimes have non-standard drain-hose routing in retrofit installations, worth visual inspection; $160–$260 reroute if needed; (4) water-level sensor / pressure switch — SMEG sensor platform different from BSH or Whirlpool; $220–$340 swap; (5) control-board drain-cycle fault — SMEG control boards are Italian-platform specific, 7-14 day part lead typical; $440–$620. Our techs approach SMEG diagnostics as distinct from BSH or Whirlpool — the platform knowledge doesn't transfer."
  },
  {
    q: "We have a SMEG FAB fridge and want the kitchen suite matched — do SMEG dishwashers come in FAB colors?",
    a: "Yes, but with nuance. SMEG's color program originated around the FAB refrigerator and has extended to broader appliance categories including dishwashers, but the color options are more limited on dishwashers than on FAB refrigerators. Typical SMEG dishwasher color options include the classic FAB palette tones (cream, black, red, pastels) but not every color offered on FAB refrigerators is available on dishwashers. Our service approach for coordinated SMEG kitchen suites: document all exterior colors of every SMEG appliance in the kitchen at intake; if any service requires exterior panel replacement or repair, we coordinate with SMEG USA to verify color-match availability and order accordingly. Color-matched exterior parts sourcing runs 7-14 days typical lead time through the Italian factory. Interior service (gaskets, drain pumps, control boards) isn't affected by exterior color and runs at standard 3-7 day lead."
  },
  {
    q: "What does SMEG dishwasher repair cost in LA?",
    a: "Residential diagnostic is $89, waived when you authorize the repair. Common SMEG bands: drain filter clean (often free at diagnostic) $89 if no other work needed; drain pump replacement $280–$420; water-inlet valve $260–$380; door latch + interlock $240–$360; door gasket (panel-ready profile) $260–$400; door gasket (FAB retro profile with specific trim integration) $320–$480; heating element $280–$440; spray arm replacement $180–$300; circulation pump $420–$620; main control board $440–$620 (7-14 day Italian parts lead typical); FAB retro trim hardware replacement quoted individually (2-6 week color-matched parts lead). SMEG service pricing runs at the upper-mid-premium tier — comparable to Miele on labor but with longer parts-lead for specialty items due to the brand's smaller US parts network compared to German luxury brands. First-visit repair rates are strong on drain + gasket + spray-arm service; control-board and color-matched trim are second-visit completion after parts arrive."
  }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "LocalBusiness",
    "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair — SMEG Dishwasher Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical,
    "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL,
    "priceRange": "$$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "serviceType": "SMEG Dishwasher Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "SMEG dishwasher repair across Los Angeles — Italian Bermani family Guastalla 1948, independent. Linea built-in 24\" panel-ready + stainless-front, FAB retro color-coordinated dishwashers. Design-forward LA installs across Silver Lake, Los Feliz, Highland Park, Mount Washington. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "priceSpecification": {
        "@type": "PriceSpecification",
        "price": "89.00",
        "priceCurrency": "USD",
        "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } }))
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "SMEG", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/smeg/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "SMEG Dishwasher Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">
    {schemaJsons.map((schema) => (
      <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />
    ))}
  </Fragment>

  <div class="call-banner">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span>SMEG dishwasher service? Same-day across LA:</span>
      <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
          <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › SMEG › Dishwasher Repair</div>
          <h1>SMEG Dishwasher Repair</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            SMEG is the Italian Bermani family's independent appliance company — founded 1948 in
            Guastalla, Emilia-Romagna, still family-controlled through three generations, with no
            corporate-parent consolidation. The FAB retro line (launched 1997) is SMEG's globally
            recognized flagship, but SMEG's Linea built-in dishwasher line serves a distinct LA design
            segment: households that specified SMEG FAB refrigeration and want coordinated appliance-
            suite aesthetic across dishwasher, range, espresso machine, and blender. Our LA SMEG
            dishwasher service concentrates in design-forward Silver Lake, Los Feliz, Highland Park,
            Mount Washington, Echo Park, and Atwater Village where the kitchen's visual identity drives
            appliance selection as much as function. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic
            waived with the repair.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
            <a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a>
          </div>
          <ul class="hero-facts">
            <li><b>Bermani family independent since 1948</b> — no corporate-parent consolidation, Guastalla factory</li>
            <li><b>Linea built-in + FAB retro</b> — both dishwasher lines serviced, color-matched parts sourcing</li>
            <li><b>Design-forward LA neighborhoods</b> — Silver Lake / Los Feliz / Highland Park volume</li>
            <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b> — waived when you authorize the repair</li>
          </ul>
        </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span>CSLB #1138898 · Insured</span>
      <span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span>
      <span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>SMEG in LA — Italian family-owned, design-forward dishwasher segment</h2>
      <p>
        SMEG's distinguishing feature in LA's dishwasher market isn't the dishwasher itself — it's the
        brand identity and design coordination that comes with a SMEG appliance-suite install. The FAB
        refrigerator (launched 1997 as SMEG's global retro flagship) drove most SMEG brand recognition
        in the US, and the dishwasher line exists primarily to complete the coordinated kitchen suite
        for households that specified FAB refrigeration and want matching design DNA across the
        dishwasher, range, small appliances (espresso machine, kettle, toaster, stand mixer). Linea
        built-in dishwashers serve this function with European-spec engineering (stainless-steel tub,
        43-47 dB noise, 24-inch standard cabinetry fit) while preserving SMEG's independent family-
        brand identity.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our LA SMEG dishwasher service territory concentrates exactly where the design-forward kitchen
        demographic concentrates: Silver Lake (vintage-modern kitchens with FAB retro as the focal
        point), Los Feliz and Echo Park (mid-century remodels with coordinated SMEG suites),
        Highland Park and Mount Washington (eclectic-modern renovations where SMEG appeals to
        design-conscious homeowners), Atwater Village (growing design-forward demographic),
        plus scattered installs in Westside design-premium kitchens (Venice, Mar Vista, Santa Monica)
        and Hollywood Hills / Beverly Hills households where the SMEG kitchen-suite spec appears alongside
        Sub-Zero or Thermador primary refrigeration. SMEG dishwasher volume is modest compared to
        Bosch / Samsung / LG mass-market, but concentrated in high-intent design-conscious households
        where the service expectation is careful attention to finish preservation and prompt parts
        sourcing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>SMEG dishwasher failures our techs see most often in LA</h2>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Drain pump + filter service</h3>
        <p>
          Standard drain-system diagnostic, but with SMEG-platform-specific parts. Filter clean often
          free at diagnostic; drain pump swap $280–$420 using SMEG-Italian-sourced parts (3-7 day
          typical lead, 7-day specialty variants).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Door latch + interlock on 6-8 year units</h3>
        <p>
          Door interlock system drifts out of calibration or mechanically fails at daily-use household
          6-8 year timeline. Swap + adjustment $240–$360. Preserves FAB retro trim integrity during
          service on color-coordinated units.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Door gasket compression on FAB-coordinated trim</h3>
        <p>
          Gasket replacement on FAB-trim-coordinated dishwasher units requires attention to color-match
          alignment and panel-seat geometry. $320–$480 depending on trim configuration. Panel-ready
          integrated units run $260–$400.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Heating element + spray arm service</h3>
        <p>
          LA hard water accelerates scale on heating elements. Element swap $280–$440. Spray arm
          replacement (upper or lower) $180–$300. Regular 6-10 year service items on daily-use SMEG
          dishwashers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Control board + interface (Italian platform specialty)</h3>
        <p>
          SMEG control boards are Italian-platform specific — don't cross-reference with BSH, Miele, or
          Whirlpool. Board swap $440–$620 with 7-14 day parts lead time typical. Interface-panel
          failures separately $320–$480 on higher-trim Linea units.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>FAB color-matched exterior panel service</h3>
        <p>
          Exterior damage to FAB-color dishwashers requires factory-matched panel replacement from
          SMEG Italy via SMEG USA distribution. Quoted individually; 2-6 week lead time typical
          depending on color. Interior service runs in parallel at standard pace.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>SMEG dishwasher product lines we service</h2>
      <div class="model-grid">
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Linea built-in 24" panel-ready</h3>
          <p>Mainstream SMEG dishwasher product for LA. European-spec built-in with stainless-steel tub,
          43-47 dB noise, panel-ready integration. LSA series and related model families.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Linea 24" stainless-front</h3>
          <p>Stainless-front variant of Linea built-in for kitchens that spec exposed dishwasher
