          Service coordination for multi-SMEG kitchens possible through combined visits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Italian-platform parts (independent from BSH / Miele / Whirlpool)</h3>
          <p>SMEG dishwasher parts don't cross-reference with broader European or US platforms.
          SMEG USA distribution (Fairfield NJ) is the parts channel. Lead time 3-7 days common, 7-14
          days specialty, 2-6 weeks color-matched retro.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Broader SMEG brand family</h3>
          <p>Beyond refrigeration and dishwashers, SMEG offers ranges, ovens, cooktops, hoods, and
          small appliances (espresso, kettle, toaster, stand mixer, blender). Kitchen-suite installs
          common in design-forward LA households.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>SMEG vs broader European dishwashers — the Italian family-brand positioning</h2>
      <p>
        SMEG occupies a specific niche in LA's premium dishwasher market that differs from the
        consolidated-European-parent alternatives.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>SMEG (independent Italian family)</b> — Bermani family Guastalla 1948, no corporate parent,
