        engineering, deepest US parts network. See <a href="/brands/miele-dishwasher-repair/">Miele
        dishwasher repair</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Bosch 800 Series (BSH)</b> — Bosch Siemens Hausgeräte consolidated European parent,
        German engineering, broad US dealer network. See <a href="/brands/bosch-dishwasher-repair/">
